title: APR 04 2022 - DISNEY ‘CAST MEMBERS’ IN FAVOR OF FL ANTI-GROOMING LAW
description:
Despite the noise made by Disney corporate and executives about their disapproval with Florida’s recently passed anti-grooming law, leaked messages from Disney ‘cast members’ reveal many are in favor. All of this as Ukrainian President Zelensky denies renouncing NATO and declaring neutrality amid German Prime Minister Scholz’s February proposal. Meanwhile, Viktor Orban declares victory in fourth consecutive landslide win as the Prime Minister of Hungary, and Shanghai continues to see COVID-19 cases rise resulting in more rigorous lockdowns.
